Title: SCUBA Diving
Prerequisites: Q3 2026.Tue Dates: 2/24, 3/3, 3/10, 3/17**, 3/31**, 4/7**, 4/14**  (** Ends in Q4). Thu Dates: 2/19, 2/26, 3/5, 3/12, 3/19**, 4/2**, 4/9**(** Ends in Q4). Meet at Alumni Wang pool/Classroom 66-160 after. All participants must complete PE&W Swim/Boat test by 2/4 to register along with passing SCUBA pre-test on day 1, able to lift 40 lbs and in good health. Must complete all documentation forms from PE&W to confirm registration by 2/9 @ 5p. Attendance is required on the first and last day.
Equipment: Bathing suit or shorts and shirt. Equipment provided by United Divers for pool sessions. A mask, booties, fins and a snorkel must be purchased for open water dives.
